window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He can’t help but fall for her - big feet and all.</p> <p>Grumpy Zach isn’t interested in settling down. He’s a lion on a mission, with no time for a mate. As if fate cares what he wants.</p> <p>An order from his king has him guarding a peculiar stowaway who might have answers to a mystery - and causes him to question his heart.</p> <p>It will take all his feline skill to keep her safe as they race to locate a dangerous treasure. As they come to rely on each other, things start to heat up.</p> <p>Until the unexpected tears them apart.</p> <p>But Zach won’t give up without a fight, because this lion knows he’s found his mate.</p>"; 
